@node Main "Triangwa - Documentation"

                             'Triangwa' V1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Triangwa' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where the goal is to move tiles
that contain triangles so their contiguous sides are parallel to
those of the triangles of neighbouring tiles. When that happens,
these tiles are then eliminated and you get points according to the
number of removed tiles.

  After a move is made, a new tile will appear on the game board.
Just be careful not to let the game board fill up completely as
that would end the game....

  Have fun!

